longBusinessSummary: Sanwaria Consumer Limited is under corporate insolvency resolution process. It was previously engaged in the manufacture and sale of rice, edible oil, and staple food products, such as pulses, sugar, soya chunks, wheat flour, rice flour, salt, suji, maida, besan, daliya, soya meal, etc. The company was incorporated in 1991 and is based in Bhopal, India.
